  <brief_title>Asymptomatic Brain Metastasis in Non-small Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase III Trial of Stereotactic Radiosurgery (SRS) Versus Observation for Patients With Asymptomatic Cerebral Oligo-metastases in Non-small Cell Lung Cancer (NSCLC)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
