  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The prognosis of NSCLC patients with asymptomatic brain metastasis, who are not treated with
      SRS or WBRT has not been fully investigated yet. This randomized phase III trial is conducted
      to determine the exact role of SRS in NSCLC patients with asymptomatic oligo brain metastases
      whether early treatment with SRS would improve survival even in patients with asymptomatic
      brain metastasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
